| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0483 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5d36f11f-c7c0-5c34-9894-bbbfac0f9dab"
